def student_list(request):
  std= Student.objects.all()
  # obeject per page
  paginator = Paginator(std,5)
  # page number
  page_number = request.GET.get('page')
  #page object
  page_obj= paginator.get_page(page_number)
  return render(request,'student.html',{'page_obj':page_obj})
